### Hadith 2:307

*Narrated*

Narrated'Abdullah:

I used to greet the Prophet while he was in prayer and he would return
my greeting, but when we returned (from Ethiopia) I greeted the Prophet
(while he was praying) but he did not return the greeting, and (after
finishing the prayer) he said, "In the prayer one is occupied (with a
more serious matter)."

